How-to install Epil for application-use :

sudo mkdir /usr/include/epil
sudo cp -r your_epil_dir/lib/usr_includes/* /usr/include/epil/
cd your_epil_dir; make lib
cp your_epil_dir/lib/epil.a apps/your_app/

Now you should be able to start your application !
Don't forget to include Epil headers like that :

#include <epil/TheHeaderFile.h*>

Header directories :

epil/
epil/utils/
epil/exceptions/